4Geeks Academy offers a comprehensive AI and Machine Learning Engineer bootcamp designed for beginners. Over 16 weeks, students attend three classes per week, learning Python, SQL, and developing predictive models using libraries like Pandas and Numpy. The curriculum covers algorithms, data-driven strategies, and the complete lifecycle of AI projects from development to deployment, ensuring security and privacy. Classes are limited to 12 participants, and the program offers certificates recognized by various organizations. Students can choose to learn in English or Spanish. For more details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop